\begin_layout Standard
Reintegration counter counts 129 consecutive ocurrences of 11 consecutive
 
\color red
recessive
\color inherit
 bits after unit turned 
\color red
bus-off
\color inherit
.
 Reintegration counter counts only during reintegration, not during initial
 
\color red
bus integration
\color inherit
